ğŸ Not to be confused with Bedok Jetty, Sungei Bedok Jetty is a recently completed double Jetty at the mouth of Sungei Bedok.
ğŸ The two parallel Jetty sit at both banks of the river with a bridge across it connecting the double Jetty.
ğŸ Anglers are seen at the end of the Jetty trying their luck.
ğŸ It's a great place to fish or simply to enjoy the sunset and sea breeze.
